{"tid":2505440,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"睡房門推門變拉門設計 搞到客飯廳無位放電視 網民稱家居裝修要斷捨離","createTime":"2021-04-26T14:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:58:07.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3553fd1ca5d62fe93234e5c5e365aa31b516ff40","tid":2505440,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"睡房門推門變拉門設計 搞到客飯廳無位放電視 網民稱家居裝修要斷捨離<br />\n22:45 2021/04/26<br />\n<br />\n&quot;香港人居住空間愈住愈細，因應樓價，上車盤面積亦變得「將價就價」，港人唯有在家居裝修上花更多心思，以增加單位空間。不少業主都會加建地台或增建閣樓。有單位原則睡房開門向內，由於要加建地枱，所以設計師改為向外，剛好遮蓋電視位置，引起網民一番討論。<br />\n<br />\n部份網民建議改用趟門設計，甚至認為不需要房門......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2940071/%E7%9D%A1%E6%88%BF%E9%96%80%E6%8E%A8%E9%96%80%E8%AE%8A%E6%8B%89%E9%96%80%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%20%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%A2%E9%A3%AF%E5%BB%B3%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E8%A6%81%E6%96%B7%E6%8D%A8%E9%9B%A2?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2940071%2F%25E7%259D%25A1%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%2520%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%2520%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%258D%25A8%25E9%259B%25A2%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B68dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=2e664c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2940071/%E7%9D%A1%E6%88%BF%E9%96%80%E6%8E%A8%E9%96%80%E8%AE%8A%E6%8B%89%E9%96%80%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%20%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%A2%E9%A3%AF%E5%BB%B3%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E8%A6%81%E6%96%B7%E6%8D%A8%E9%9B%A2?mtc=60